<template><div><h1 id="hasownproperty" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#hasownproperty"><span>hasOwnProperty</span></a></h1>
<p><code v-pre>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty</code> 方法用于检测指定对象自有 <code v-pre>Properties</code> 中是否具有指定的 <code v-pre>Property</code>。</p>
<h2 id="语法" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#语法"><span>语法</span></a></h2>
<p>语法：</p>
<div class="language-js line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="js" data-title="js" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre v-pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#E5C07B">obj</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">.</span><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">hasOwnProperty</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">(</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#E06C75">v</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">);</span></span>
